#103
jaggar~
Jaggar~
The last thing you see was a blur moving towards you.
~
Noted as the Angel of Death, there isn't one person alive who can withstand
an attack from his famed daggers... But fortunately for the world, his interest
in money and politics is quite saturated... All he cares about is the protection
of a loved one...
~
