#104
altima~
Altima~
A powerful winged figure is here wielding a massive blade.
~
One of the most infamous avengers ever, Saint Altima had a humble beginning...
but alas, she was corrupted for the crave for power and destruction and for many
years had the earth into turmoil... until a group of braver fighters showed her
the error of her ways.
Now sitting beside Tyrael, her only wish is to save Mankind.
~
